invalid type: string "Particulars Details \nTax Benefit Available under Section 80C \n \n3. Objectives of the Scheme \nThe major objectives of Sukanya Samriddhi Yojana are: \n1. Financial Security for Girl Child \nTo build a financial corpus for future educational and marriage expenses. \n2. Encourage Savings \nTo develop long-term saving habits among families. \n3. Promote Girl Child Welfare \n’’